Bare Metal servers

A bare metal server - dedicated physical servers

dedicated to a single customers

server plugged into rack in data servers
cloud provider managed server up to OS

will fix rack connection, reboot

customer is responsible for managing everything else on servers

bare metal server can be preconfigured or custom configured

ram, os, components

customers can install their own OS, or own hypervisiors

bare metal servers can add GPU - help scientific computing

bare metal servers - high performance, big data analytics, ERP, AI, virtualization

bare metal vs virtualized

bare metal - virtual and high performance, compliance, control and transparency

virtual servers - low cost, limited in performance
